  <brief_title>Electrical Impedance Scanning of Thyroid Nodules Prior to Thyroid Surgery: a Prospective Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Electrical Impedance Scanning of Thyroid Nodules Prior to Thyroid Surgery: a Prospective Study</official_title>
