  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients over the age of 18 with thyroid nodules scheduled for surgery will undergo EIS scan.
      Each node will be scanned and graded form 1-5 (1=benign, 5=malignant). Results will be
      compared with final histopathology.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
